item.title: Ann Arbor Web Analytics Wednesday planning
item.description: I'm working with a few other folks on setting up a relatively regular local group that has discussions of tools like Google Analytics and other systems used to instrument web sites and web applications. We're looking at a date in January 2014 to start, and a Wednesday as the day of the week we think might work best. Let me know if you're interested, or join the Ann Arbor Web Analytics Wednesday meetup.
